  "body": "Now:\r\ncfg.forkValidator.NotifyCurrentHeight is in StageFinish - before commit\r\nMeans it may cause race: CL will be notified, will create some request to EL about new block, but will not see any data - because tx.Commit() is not done yet.\r\n\r\nNeed move it after tx.Commit. See other notifications in `StageLoopStep`\r\n\r\nProbably need do after https://github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/issues/5627\r\n\r\n",
